00</in-bse-fin:SegmentFinanceCosts><in-bse-fin:SegmentFinanceCosts contextRef="FourD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">33218000</in-bse-fin:SegmentFinanceCosts><in-bse-fin:OtherUnallocableExpenditureNetOffUnAllocableIncome contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">0</in-bse-fin:OtherUnallocableExpenditureNetOffUnAllocableIncome><in-bse-fin:OtherUnallocableExpenditureNetOffUnAllocableIncome contextRef="FourD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">0</in-bse-fin:OtherUnallocableExpenditureNetOffUnAllocableIncome><in-bse-fin:SegmentProfitBeforeTax contextRef="OneD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">140139000</in-bse-fin:SegmentProfitBeforeTax><in-bse-fin:SegmentProfitBeforeTax contextRef="FourD" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">149359000</in-bse-fin:SegmentProfitBeforeTax><in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment contextRef="OneReportable31D">Pharmaceuticals</in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment><in-bse-fin:SegmentAssets contextRef="OneReportable31I" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">1453201000</in-bse-fin:SegmentAssets><in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment contextRef="OneReportable32D">Electronics</in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment><in-bse-fin:SegmentAssets contextRef="OneReportable32I" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">411298000</in-bse-fin:SegmentAssets><in-bse-fin:SegmentAssets contextRef="OneI" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">1864499000</in-bse-fin:SegmentAssets><in-bse-fin:UnAllocableAssets contextRef="OneI" unitRef="INR" decimals="-5">0</in-bse-fin:UnAllocableAssets><in-bse-fin:NetSegmentAssets contextRef="OneI" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">1864499000</in-bse-fin:NetSegmentAssets><in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment contextRef="OneReportable41D">Pharmaceuticals</in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment><in-bse-fin:SegmentLiabilities contextRef="OneReportable41I" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">992241000</in-bse-fin:SegmentLiabilities><in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment contextRef="OneReportable42D">Electronics</in-bse-fin:DescriptionOfReportableSegment><in-bse-fin:SegmentLiabilities contextRef="OneReportable42I" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">116826000</in-bse-fin:SegmentLiabilities><in-bse-fin:SegmentLiabilities contextRef="OneI" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">1109067000</in-bse-fin:SegmentLiabilities><in-bse-fin:NetSegmentLiabilities contextRef="OneI" unitRef="INR" decimals="-3">1109067000</in-bse-fin:NetSegmentLiabilities><in-bse-fin:DisclosureOfNotesOnSegmentsExplanatoryTextBlock contextRef="OneD">1.	Considering the nature of the Company's business and operations, as well as based on reviews performed by Chief operating decision maker regarding resource allocation and performance management, the Company has identified following as reportable segments in accordance with the requirements of Ind AS 108 - Operating Segments.										 &lt;BR&gt; 
2.	Classification of Business Segments:						 &lt;BR&gt; 
